   The main image shows two structures.

   * **Structure 2 (the rocket-like one):** Consists of a red circular base block, a red triangular block sitting on top of it, a yellow curved block sitting on the triangle, a slightly darker orange triangular block on top of the yellow block, and finally, two slightly lighter orange triangular blocks on top of the darker orange block.  There are 7 blocks. 3 layers.
